    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is starting to brown, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
