    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>tortiglioni</strong> to the dish with a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[750ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Nestle the <strong>tortiglioni</strong> into the water as much as you can, then stir everything together and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
